FBIS4-21768 "jptot014__l94068" JPRS-TOT-94-014-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 29 March 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA INDIA `Top Terrorist' Surrenders to Police in Punjab `Top Terrorist' Surrenders to Police in Punjab BK2903104594 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 0830 GMT 29 Mar 94 BK2903104594 Delhi All India Radio Network English BFN [Text] In Punjab, a top terrorist -- Ramesh Kanwar Singh, alias Pir Singh -- has surrendered before the police. Presenting him before newsmen at a press conference in Chandigarh today, the director general of police, Mr. K.P.S. Gill, said that Kanwar Singh had been a member of many militant organizations and had remained in Pakistan for seven years.
